## Design Notes for Demo

- Background: --bg-root (#121118)
- Cards: --bg-card (#1e1c26), border --border-default (#2c2a38)
- Primary CTA: --mustard (#e8b820) background, dark text
- Provider card accent bar: --cyan-vivid (#12b4c8)
- Admin badge: --hot-pink (#f0186e)
- Patient badge: --cyan-vivid (#12b4c8)
- Font: Space Grotesk for headings (load from Google Fonts), Inter for body
- Section eyebrows: font-mono, uppercase, letter-spacing 0.1em, --text-muted
- "HealthStack" logo: Space Grotesk bold, --mustard accent on "Health"
- Booking confirmation: large checkmark in --parrot-green (#6ed46a)
- Stripe checkout modal: dark modal overlay, card input with mono font,
  Stripe logo (text only), payment button --mustard

